1.1  stop the service of mongodb -> systemctl stop mongod.service

1.2  check this service and it is enable means do disable why beacuse it will automatically start the service--> systemctl disable mongod.service

1.3  to remove the all mongodb packages ---> dnf remove mongodb-org*

1.4  to delete the data directory the path of data directory is :-- /var/lib/mongo
1.5 to remove logs we have path :-(/var/log/mongodb/mongod.log) 
1.6 to delete configration file :- /etc/mongod.conf
1.7 to remove repo file and the file location inside the system configration file:-- /etc/yum.repo.d/mongodb-org-8.0  | dnf repolist
1.8 to clean all domain name system file :- yum clean all







